title: Whitney, my love
content:
AS THEIR ELEGANT TRAVELLING CHAISE ROCKED AND
SWAYED along the rutted country road, Lady Anne Gilbert leaned
her cheek against her husband's shoulder and heaved a long,
impatient sigh. "Another whole hour until we arrive, and already the
suspense is positively gnawing at me. I keep wondering what
Whitney will be like now that she's grown up."
author: Judith Mcnaught

title: The Creation of the Universe,
content: In the beginning, the universe was shaped by the will of the gods. From the cosmic void, they brought light, matter, and life. The creation stories of various cultures intertwine to tell a story of divine craftsmanship and cosmic order.
author: kxjfnbu

title: Reducers
content:
Actions describe the fact that something needs to be happened, but don't specify how the application's state changes in response. This is the job of reducers.
Reducers specify how the state changes in response to Actions. All Reducers must be pure functions:
•
They produce the same output given the same input
•
They don’t mutate state
author: Asaad

title: Flux Architecture and Redux
content:
Redux architecture is a predictable state management pattern, centralizing the application's state in a single store and enabling consistent state updates through unidirectional data flow and pure reducer functions.
The data flows in a unidirectional cycle: actions are dispatched to describe state changes, reducers process these actions to compute a new state, and a new updated state is produced, which then notifies subscribed components to re-render.
author: qwerty
